35
00:06:24,220 --> 00:06:27,548
Now, the AZAN should be
ALLAH-O AKBAR, ALLAH-O AKBAR

36
00:06:27,548 --> 00:06:34,240
ALLAH-O AKBAR, ALLAH-O AKBAR, La Elaha Ella Allah. This is the AZAN. So, the AZAN or the call for

